    <thetext>Description of problem:

In some cases, especially when controlled by NM, wpa_supplicant may fail to detect external MAC changes, leading to a timeout when associating to an AP.


Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):

wpa_supplicant-2.6-6.fc26


How reproducible:

30% of the times on my laptop


Steps to Reproduce:
1. enable MAC address randomization in NM
2. try to connect to a Wi-Fi network


Actual results:

Connection fails with timeout


Expected results:

Connection succeeds


Additional info:

Upstream fix: https://w1.fi/cgit/hostap/commit/?id=290834df69556b903b49f2a45671cc62b44f13bb</thetext>
